window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The apocalypse is here!</b></p> <p>After the world changed and aliens started hunting down humans, only a small group of survivors remain. But the alien invasion is just getting started! Now our heroes must learn to work with the AI and nanotech provided by Lucy to grow stronger.</p> <p>The seeders and other monsters they encountered so far were just the first wave. Now the real aliens are going to arrive to claim parts of earth. Brad, Jake, and Sam must level up if they are going to survive the second wave!</p> <p>Apocalypse Online is a LitRPG/GameLit post-apocalypse fantasy series filled with action, adventure, aliens and snarky AIs.</p> <p>If you are a fan of System Apocalypse, Defiance of the Fall, or the Sun Shadow series, you'll love Apocalypse Online!</p>"; 
